          You can find the full release notes on the
          <a href="/en/release-notes" style="color:#3182ce;font-weight:600;">Release Notes</a> page
          or directly on
          <a href="https://github.com/ankaios76/gonopbx/releases/tag/v1.6.0" style="color:#3182ce;font-weight:600;" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GitHub</a>.
        </p>

